# npm root .npmignore does not override package.json "files"; this subdirectory
# ignore file keeps local template smoke-test residue out of source packs.
**/tmp/**
**/temp/**
**/node_modules/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/coverage/**
**/.next/**
**/out/**

**/.serena/**
**/.codebase-memory/**
**/.codex/sessions/**
**/.codex/memories/**
**/.codex/cache/**
**/.codex/logs/**
**/.codex/auth*
**/.codex/*.local.toml

*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.msi
*.exe
*.dmg
